@host = http://localhost:38765

### 获取对话列表
POST {{host}}/api/conversations
Content-Type: application/json

###

### 获取消息列表
POST {{host}}/api/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": 1
}

###

### 发送消息
POST {{host}}/api/send-message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "conversationId": 1,
  "senderId": 0,
  "senderType": "me",
  "content": "测试消息"
}

###

### 给测试机器人发送消息
POST {{host}}/api/bot/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "content": "测试机器人消息 4"
}



